### QR Code Generation and Validation Test
### This file contains test requests for the QR code functionality

### 1. Create a booking (this will generate a QR code)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/Bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "customerNic": "123456789V",
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "customerEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
  "customerPhone": "+94771234567",
  "stationId": "STATION_ID_HERE",
  "slotId": "SLOT_ID_HERE",
  "reservationStartTime": "2024-12-20T10:00:00Z",
  "durationMinutes": 120,
  "estimatedKWh": 25.5,
  "notes": "Test booking for QR code generation"
}

### 2. Validate QR code (replace with actual booking data)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/Bookings/validateQR
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "bookingId": "BOOKING_ID_HERE",
  "evOwnerNIC": "123456789V",
  "stationId": "STATION_ID_HERE",
  "reservationDate": "2024-12-20T10:00:00Z"
}

### 3. Get booking details to see QR code
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Bookings/BOOKING_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

